 ##AI Employee Payroll & Workforce Management System

## 📌 Project Overview

The AI Employee Payroll & Workforce Management System is a full-stack web application designed to automate and simplify employee payroll operations inside an organization. The system helps HR departments manage employee records, salary structures, payroll processing, leave approvals, tax calculations, and payslip generation efficiently.

This project reduces manual payroll errors, minimizes paperwork, improves transparency, and increases workforce management efficiency through automation and analytics.

The system provides secure role-based access for Admins, HR Managers, and Employees using JWT authentication and modern web technologies.

---

# 🚀 Project Title

## AI Employee Payroll & Workforce Management System

---

# ❗ Problem Statement

Many organizations still manage payroll operations manually using spreadsheets or outdated systems. Manual payroll management creates several problems such as:

- Salary calculation errors
- Incorrect tax deductions
- Delayed salary processing
- Difficulty in managing employee leave records
- Lack of transparency for employees
- Time-consuming HR operations
- Data redundancy and security issues

To solve these challenges, the AI Employee Payroll & Workforce Management System is developed as a centralized platform that automates payroll calculations, leave tracking, employee management, and payslip generation while providing secure and scalable workforce management.

